{"type": "article", "id": 2908, "title": "ULTRAOLIVE 防水包", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-17T08:04:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000636xkVM3yFAbUNCEHYt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纽约包袋品牌 ULTRAOLIVE 素来主打实用性和功能性，日前，他们推出一款全新设计的防水包，选用了具有防水性能的棉质布料，缝合边沿也考虑到了防水的需求，为包内的随身物提供了全方位的保护。该款包型大小适中，内部空间足够装入一双球鞋，提供黑色与薄荷色两色可选，定价 55 美元，<a href=\"http://www.ultraolive.com/products/taped-seam-dry-bag-ice-blue\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000634jzvypSYXJM3s7BWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000635MADQ3fEGYiWaStcV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060006350OdHfP8BVzR35C2E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}